name: Foundation Token
additional_notices:
The following token has a variable tax function on the smart contract to change tax rates post deployment.
Do your own research and be careful if you are trading this token.

description.en:
What is the project about?
Foundation have a utility for a fully decentralized protocol for private transactions on Ethereum and BSC.

What makes your project unique?
Foundation is a revolutionary crypto mixer token that serves as a utility to reduce fees when using the mixer. Additionally, the token has a decentralized autonomous organization (DAO) component deployed on fnddao.foundationtoken.io , where holders can vote on proposals to improve the ecosystem..
Foundation is also working on an NFT AI minting project, where AI will generate full NFT collections for use by anyone
Foundation also has a blockchain and a swap aggregator coming to help with privacy and anonymity.




History of your project.


What’s next for your project?
NFT marketplace
BSC Blockchain
CEX exchange listings
Short Selling dex

What can your token be used for?
Trading tokens 
Voting 
Staking rewards
Swap functional
